get comment date "MAY 2013" WordPress Codex "Function Reference"
================================================================

NAME
----

get comment date - Retrieve the comment date of the current comment.

SYNOPSIS
--------

Retrieve the comment date of the current comment.

USAGE
-----

` <?php get_comment_date( $d, $comment_ID ); ?> `

### Parameters

 `$d` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) date() format description.
    Default: get\_option('date\_format')

 `$comment_ID` 
:   ([*int*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#Int "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) Valid comment id
    Default: None

\

### Returns

 (String) 
:   Formatted comment date.

### Examples

    <?php 

    $d = "d.m.Y H:i:s";
    $comment_date = get_comment_date( $d, $comment_ID );
    echo $comment_date;

    ?>

### Uses

Calls 'get\_comment\_date' hook with the formatted date and the \$d
parameter respectively

Uses \$comment

